'''全國州長協會'''（{{lang-en|National Governors Association}}，縮寫：{{lang|en|NGA}}），是建立於1908年的[[美國|美國]]無黨派政治組織，由全國50個[[美国州份|州份]]的州長以及5個[[美国领地|領地]]的總督組成，依靠各州繳交的會費、聯邦資助和合約、以及私人資金資助營運。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nga.org/cms/home/about/faq/col2-content/main-content-list/f-how-are-nga-and-the-nga-center.html |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2020-11-02 |archive-date=2013-12-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131214204131/http://www.nga.org/cms/home/about/faq/col2-content/main-content-list/f-how-are-nga-and-the-nga-center.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

[[File:Secretary_Pompeo_Delivers_Remarks_to_the_National_Governors_Association_2020_Winter_Meeting_(49506943613).jpg|thumb]][[邁克·蓬佩奧|邁克·蓬佩奧]]正在全國州長協會2020年冬季大會發言]]
1907年，{{le|內陸水道委員會|Inland Waterways Commission}}認為有需要諮詢{{le|州長會議|Conference of Governors}}與[[进步时代|进步时代]]中應用和管理天然資源有關的實務問題，以獲取各州以至全國的意見。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ebooksread.com/authors-eng/united-states-inland-waterways-commission/preliminary-report-of-the-inland-waterways-commission-message-from-the-presiden-tin/page-4-preliminary-report-of-the-inland-waterways-commission-message-from-the-presiden-tin.shtml |title=內陸水道委員會正在進行的調查 |quote=Letter to the President, October 5, 1907: ..."3. We are of opinion that the conference may best be held in the national capital next winter, and that the conferees should comprise the governors of all our States and Territories, a limited number of delegates to be appointed by each governor, and representatives from leading organizations of both State and national scope engaged in dealing with natural resources or with practical questions relating thereto... In his Memphis address on October 4 the President announced the intention of calling such a conference, and on November 13 he issued invitations to the governors of the States and Territories to meet at the White House May 13–15, 1908;..." |language=en |accessdate=2020-11-02 |archive-date=2019-11-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191117165321/http://www.ebooksread.com/authors-eng/united-states-inland-waterways-commission/preliminary-report-of-the-inland-waterways-commission-message-from-the-presiden-tin/page-4-preliminary-report-of-the-inland-waterways-commission-message-from-the-presiden-tin.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>此舉開設了每年州長會面的先例，當時的州長會議由[[美国总统|美国总统]][[西奥多·罗斯福|西奥多·罗斯福]]資助舉行，時至現今則由全國州長協會舉辦。<ref>[http://www.theodoreroosevelt.org/life/conConf.htm Conservation Commissions and Conferences under the Roosevelt Administration 1901-1909] {{Wayback|url=http://www.theodoreroosevelt.org/life/conConf.htm |date=20120426182331 }}, Theodore Roosevelt Association</ref>協會功用主要是成為[[美國聯邦政府|聯邦政府]]與{{le|美國州政府|State governments of the United States|州政府}}之間的[[公共政策|公共政策]]聯繫渠道，如代表各州在[[国会山|-{zh-cn:国会山;zh-hant:國會山莊}-]]和[[白宮|白宮]]討論聯邦事務、制定各州施政計劃的政策報告、主持[[社会网络|網絡研討會]]等。

協會主席一職每年在[[民主党_(美国)|民主]]、[[共和黨_(美國)|共和]]兩黨之間輪替，副主席則是主席友黨成員擔任，翌屆就任主席。

